title: Shakespearean Dialogues Collection 002
creator: William Shakespeare
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Shakespearean Dialogues Collection 002. This is the second LibriVox collection of scenes from Shakespeare's plays, mainly comprising dialogues between two characters. The theme for this collection is "Women's Worlds," as the excerpts are all scenes between female characters. (Summary by Elizabeth Klett) For more free audio books, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; audio; shakespeare; dialogue; women
